Create the following three enums in loanflow-common under src/main/java/com/loanflow/common/enums. These are the API contract versions of domain enums used in request and response DTOs. The loan-service entity layer owns its own JPA-annotated enums under com.loanflow.loanservice.entity.enums and a mapper converts between them.

