LoanStatus.java:
public enum LoanStatus { SUBMITTED, PENDING_DOCUMENTS, UNDERWRITING_IN_PROGRESS, PENDING_REVIEW, APPROVED, REJECTED }

EmploymentStatus.java:
public enum EmploymentStatus { FULL_TIME, PART_TIME, SELF_EMPLOYED, UNEMPLOYED, RETIRED }

Do not add @Enumerated, @Column, or any jakarta.persistence annotations.

Create com.loanflow.common.dto.PagedResponse in loanflow-common under src/main/java/com/loanflow/common/dto:

@Getter
@Builder
@NoArgsConstructor
@AllArgsConstructor
@JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)
public class PagedResponse<T> {
    private List<T> content;
    private int page;
    private int size;
    private long totalElements;
    private int totalPages;
}

This class is the shared pagination envelope reused across all service search and list endpoints.

